values = (
{
language = ENG;
value = "Cantata is a high contrast extended Didone style text face. In addition to being useful in medium to large text sizes, Seigal is meant to evoke luxury when used in display sizes. Seigal was originally inspired by hand written letters made with a pointed pen on an old map handmade map of NYC.";
